text: Abdur Rahman Fakir is a Bangladesh Jamaat-e-Islami politician and the former Member of Parliament of Bogra-6. ==Career== Fakir was elected to parliament from Bogra-6 as a Bangladesh Jamaat-e-Islami candidate in 1986. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Jamaat-e-Islami politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Abdur Rahman Fakir
